On Thu, 10 Aug 2000, Anandavel P wrote:
> 
> I want to use kudzu ( Redhat 6.2) to automatically install/configure my
> NIC. Are there any documentation/help available on this? Web search did
> not get me any useful results & the man page is of only limited use.
Post this to the RH list. Kudzu only loads the NIC driver if it is PCI I
believe. 
Loading a driver for ISA required manual intervention, and if it is PnP,
use pnpdump / isapnp.
